name: Trying to look Away, but keep coming back…
description:
You know, 
Somethings just stick with you
No matter what you do 

I find things while creating, while disappearing in forms and tunes, between the strokes in digital worlds I create a space to breath fresh air, and although, I sometimes have to go home and face the facts… I know I can always return safely to my sacred flow inside my heart & head. 

All time is well spend 
When I spend it with you.

XXX
